+# Generated API client policy
+
+Source Candidate Sprout: `sprout_b9fd056e1923a33a`
+
+When adding or changing fields in the generated API client, update `api/openapi.yaml` as the source of truth, run `pnpm generate:api` to regenerate `generated/api-client.ts`, then run `pnpm test` and `pnpm check:generated`.
+
+Do not edit `generated/api-client.ts` directly.
